  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Engineering</li><li>Position Title: <strong>QC Technician</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tampines</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon to Fri 9AM – 7PM, Sat 9AM – 1PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $2,200 + AWS + Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform in-process, final, and incoming inspections of precision parts using measurement tools such as calipers, micrometers, height gauges, and CMM machines.</li><li>Carry out dimensional and visual inspections to ensure products conform to engineering drawings and customer specifications.</li><li>Record inspection results accurately on quality forms and maintain proper documentation for traceability and audits.</li><li>Detect and report non-conformities or defects, and assist in root cause analysis and corrective actions.</li><li>Ensure adherence to quality procedures, work instructions, and safety standards throughout the production process.</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year working experience in related field</li><li>Candidates with Mechanical Engineering background are preferred</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77167 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
